import { Drawer, List, ListItemButton, ListItemIcon, ListItemText } from '@mui/material'
import React, { useState } from 'react'

const DrawerComp = () => {
    const [openDrawer, setopenDrawer] = useState(false)
  return (
    <React.Fragment>
        <Drawer open={true}>
            <List>
               <ListItemButton>
                <ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText>
                    Login
                </ListItemText>
                </ListItemIcon>
               </ListItemButton>
            </List>
        </Drawer>
    </React.Fragment>
  )
}

export default DrawerComp
